SELECT DISTINCT  '"'||v0.flight_id||'"', '"'||v1.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v2.city_code||'"', '"'||v2.city_name||'"', '"'||v3.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v4.city_code||'"', '"'||v4.city_name||'"',
 '"'||v5.state_code||'"' FROM flight v0, airport_service v1,
 city v2, airport_service v3, city v4, state v5 
WHERE (((v0.from_airport = ANY v1.airport_code) 
AND ((v1.city_code = ANY v2.city_code) 
AND (v2.city_name = 'ATLANTA'))) AND ((v0.to_airport = ANY v3.airport_code) 
AND ((v3.city_code = ANY v4.city_code) 
AND ((v4.city_name = 'WASHINGTON') AND ((v4.state_code = ANY v5.state_code) 
AND (v5.state_code = 'DC'))))));
